Package anidbcmdc.util

Class Summary
FileUtils Title: FileUtils Description: A File utility class which provides some advanced functions on files.
HashFile Title: HashFile Description: Offers all kinds of hash algorithms for file.
MiscUtils Title: MiscUtils Description: Some misc utils like add an array to an ArrayList or merge two Arrays.
RegexFilter Title: WildcardFilter Description: Checks if a filename is matched by a String.
UdpConnection Title: UdpConnection Description: Creates a connection with an udp server and sends and receives packets.
WebsiteParser Title: WebsiteParser Description: Downloads a website and searches for data surrounded by two Strings.
